<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
Intelligence (INT) is the stat affecting failure rate for this skill. <h3 id="head-3f745de841435de82ac96fcf75fc9dc7f43c0112">Udun Spells</h3>
<p>
The Udun school of magic contains spells where the corrupted forces of <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fIntroduction_20to_20the_20Gods_20of_20ToME#head-11984558524ce4f53bb86d4d76084fe577fef244"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Melkor Bauglir</a> are used to create the final spell effect. 
</p>
<p>
The Udun school is available only to a worshipper of <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fIntroduction_20to_20the_20Gods_20of_20ToME#head-11984558524ce4f53bb86d4d76084fe577fef244"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Melkor Bauglir</a>. They will also need some proficiency in the magic schools of <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fMana"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Mana</a>, <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fNature"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Nature</a>, <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fConveyance"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Conveyance</a>, and <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fFire"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Fire</a> (or alternatively <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic#sorcery"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Sorcery</a>) to cast the Udun spells. On the other hand the spell power of Udun spells is greatly increased by the character level of the caster. 
</p>
<p>
There are four <strong>combined school</strong> spells available for the Udun school: 
</p>

    <ol type="1">

    <li>
<p>
<strong>Drain</strong> (dual school: Udun/Mana level 1) Drains the mana contained in wands, staves and rods to increase yours. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 Your Udun and <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fMana"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Mana</a> skills must have reached a combined average level of 1 in order to cast this spell. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>


    <li>
<p>
<strong>Genocide</strong> (dual school: Udun/Nature level 25) Genocides all monsters of a race on the level. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 At level 10 it can genocide all monsters near you. 
</p>
</li>
                <li>
<p>
 Your Udun and <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fNature"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Nature</a> skills must have reached a combined average level of 25 in order to cast this spell. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>


    <li>
<p>
<strong>Wraithform</strong> (dual school: Udun/Conveyance level 30) Turns you temporarily into an immaterial being. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 Your Udun and <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fConveyance"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Conveyance</a> skills must have reached a combined average level of 30 in order to cast this spell. 
</p>
</li>

                </ul>


    <li>
<p>
<strong>Flame of Udun</strong> (dual school: Udun/Fire level 35) Turns you temporarily into a powerful Balrog. 
</p>
</li>

                <ul>

                <li>
<p>
 Your Udun and <a class="interwiki" title="Self" href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fFire"><img src="./wiki/rightsidebar/img/moin-inter.png" alt="[Self]" height="16" width="16">Fire</a> skills must have reached a combined average level of 35 in order to cast this spell. 
</p>
</li>
</ol>

</ul>

